data.description: Convenient South Lake Tahoe location. Perfect starter home or future vacation spot for all of your Tahoe adventures. Remodeled inside and out. Newer roof. Front and back decks as well as a fenced back yard.Completely remodeled open concept kitchen with stainless steel appliances, Corian countertops and updated light fixtures. Double pane windows all through out the house. A four star furnace with registers in every room. Very modern espresso vinyl flooring throughout living area and hallway. There is also a good sized shed in the side yard for extra storage.
